#: introduction.html:30, 106
msgid "What is Ubuntu MATE?"
msgstr "Què és l'Ubuntu MATE?"

#: introduction.html:45
msgid ""
"Ubuntu MATE is an operating system -- the core software that runs your "
"computer, similar to"
msgstr ""
"L'Ubuntu MATE és un sistema operatiu - el programari nucli que fa funcionar "
"el seu ordinador, similar al"

#: introduction.html:48
msgid "Microsoft's Windows"
msgstr "Windows de Microsoft"

#: introduction.html:50
